subtitle: Bravado Dorado
content:
Sometimes you need to escape the humdrum 9-5 of a ruthless crimelord. The solution? The dependable Bravado Dorado, SUV of the regular joe.

Leave your executive contracts and deadly deals behind as you strap into the exotic thrill of a mental breakdown in gridlocked rush hour traffic. Oh, how the other half livesâ€¦

Now available from Southern San Andreas Super Autos.
